Whisk together @unsweetened cocoa powder{2%tbsp} @sugar{2%tbsp}, @kosher salt{pinch}, and about 2tbsp @milk{1%cup} in a small saucepan over medium-low heat until cocoa and sugar are dissolved. Whisk in the rest of the milk and heat it over medium heat, whisking occasionally, until it is hot. Stir in @vanilla extract{1%tsp} and serve.
